{"tid":1689700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點揀罷邊間餐廳?","createTime":"2019-11-03T03:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T03:09:07.000Z","uid":62487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"25b4cb46b619c81db31419ac1d250759c13e27e9","tid":1689700,"uid":62487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"好簡單,邊個接警察單,就罷邊間<br />\n你話唔知個外賣仔係邊間餐廳,好簡單<br />\n直接問佢係邊間餐廳佢無理由唔答<br />\n再唔係嘅直接跟佢返去<br />\n<br />\n唔洗裝修唔洗鬧人<br />\n幫間餐廳出名令佢無生意做就夠<br />\n罷食直到餐廳主動貼出公示話唔再做警察生意<br />\n到依步就需要原諒<br />\n否則d人見到跪低之後都唔會有返生意<br />\n只會越企越硬,變到有反效果<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以話擺食到佢汁笠為止<br />\n得唔係唔得,但第一送外賣罪不至死<br />\n第二同令餐廳切割,唔再做警察生意成效比較無乜分別<br />\n仲令我地多咗支持者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/73076357_3305280702832454_6310721239014965248_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_oc=AQkRXri0wb4HxDYn4Lye6RU6uTfIodl-QGU9vXfOOZkiU5gZSV5qvEJhWPzOWqYmSeg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=f02e867f713ccbb98f470c7867c91372&amp;oe=5E597F44\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F73076357_3305280702832454_6310721239014965248_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_oc%3DAQkRXri0wb4HxDYn4Lye6RU6uTfIodl-QGU9vXfOOZkiU5gZSV5qvEJhWPzOWqYmSeg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Df02e867f713ccbb98f470c7867c91372%26oe%3D5E597F44&h=bbda174b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/photos/a.1105389652821581/3305280699499121/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcityusu.cbc%2Fphotos%2Fa.1105389652821581%2F3305280699499121%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpG6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=c621033f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/photos/a.1105389652821581/3305280699499121/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"}]}